SELECT geonames_admin1_name,count(*) AS nb
FROM wda_vigilo_observations 
WHERE obs_ts >= $__from / 1000  and obs_ts < $__to /1000  AND geonames_admin1_name IN (${region:sqlstring}) AND cat_name IN (${category:sqlstring})
GROUP BY geonames_admin1_name
ORDER BY nb DESC

targets.rawSql:
-- 24h => 86400
-- week =>604800
-- 30 days => 2592000
SELECT  cast((obs_ts / ($__interval_ms / 1000) ) as bigint) * ($__interval_ms / 1000)*1000 AS ts_in_milliseconds,count(*) AS nb
FROM wda_vigilo_observations 
WHERE obs_ts >= $__from / 1000  and obs_ts < $__to /1000  AND geonames_name IN (${quartier:sqlstring}) AND cat_name IN (${category:sqlstring})
GROUP BY ts_in_milliseconds

FROM wda_vigilo_observations

SELECT cat_name as category,count(*) AS nb
FROM wda_vigilo_observations 
WHERE obs_ts >= $__from / 1000  and obs_ts < $__to /1000  AND geonames_name IN (${quartier:sqlstring}) AND cat_name IN (${category:sqlstring})
GROUP BY category
ORDER BY nb DESC
